Building and Running iPic3D with Split Execution on Xeon and Xeon Phi
---------------------------------------------------------------------

This version of iPic3D runs the particles solver on Xeon Phi and the fields
solver on Xeon CPUs.

For instructions on how to build and run the code, visit the directories
below in the given order:

  build.xeon
  build.xeonphi

Each directory has a "HOWTO" file with detailed instructions.
